    dc:description "Figure 1. Cuernavaca inexacta (Walker) (MLPA) Male: (A) habitus,dorsolateral view; (E) genito-anal segments,left lateral view. Female: (B) habitus, dorsolateral view; (C) ventral view; (D) apex of hind leg (post tibial apical teeth and tarsi); (F) genito-anal segments, left lateral view;(G) genito-anal segments,ventral view. Scale bars:A-D:5 mm;E:0.5 mm;F-G:1 mm." ;
